foundry (0.1.1-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * New features
    - Support for builds in buildroots
    - Scripts for connecting bots over SSH
    - Configuration file and script for starting and stoping
    - Bot for sending notifications to Slack
  * Bugfixes
    - Don't send notifications when a HEAD could not be fetched
    - Make watchbot clean up IPC endpoints upon exit

 -- Matthias Kruk <m@m10k.eu>  Wed, 25 Jan 2023 17:04:37 +0900


